trans-unit.source: Represents a stored procedure in the data store.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en lagrad procedur i datalagret.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerDataStoredProcedure class is one of several types that represent the schema of a data store at design-time.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DesignerDataStoredProcedure är en av flera typer som representerar schemat för ett datalager i designläge.

trans-unit.source: These schema items are made available to controls by designers implementing the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment> interface.
trans-unit.target: Objekten schemat görs tillgängliga för kontroller av designers som implementerar det <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment>gränssnittet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment>

trans-unit.source: Controls access schema objects by calling the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment.GetConnectionSchema%2A> method of the interface.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerar åtkomst schemaobjekt genom att anropa den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment.GetConnectionSchema%2A>-metoden i gränssnittet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDataEnvironment.GetConnectionSchema%2A>

trans-unit.source: The DesignerDataStoredProcedure class represents a single table in the data store.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DesignerDataStoredProcedure representerar en enda tabell i datalagret.

trans-unit.source: A collection of DesignerDataStoredProcedure objects is returned when you call the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDesignerDataSchema.GetSchemaItems%2A> method with the `schemaClass` parameter set to <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataSchemaClass.StoredProcedures?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: En samling DesignerDataStoredProcedure objekt returneras när du anropar den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDesignerDataSchema.GetSchemaItems%2A>metod med den `schemaClass` parametern värdet <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataSchemaClass.StoredProcedures?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataSchemaClass.StoredProcedures?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.IDesignerDataSchema.GetSchemaItems%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure"></xref> class with the specified name.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure"> </xref> klass med det angivna namnet.

trans-unit.source: The name of the stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på den lagrade proceduren.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure"></xref> class with the specified name and owner.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure"> </xref> klass med det angivna namnet och ägare.

trans-unit.source: The name of the stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på den lagrade proceduren.

trans-unit.source: The data store owner of the stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: Data store ägaren av den lagrade proceduren.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, returns a collection of parameters for the stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en mängd med parametrar för den lagrade proceduren när åsidosätts i en härledd klass.

trans-unit.source: The CreateParameters method is called the first time the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure.Parameters%2A> property is accessed to populate the collection of stored-procedure parameters.
trans-unit.target: CreateParameters-metoden anropas för första gången den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure.Parameters%2A>egenskapen används för att fylla mängden lagrade procedurparametrar.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure.Parameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataParameter"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: En samling <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataParameter"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar namnet på den lagrade proceduren.

trans-unit.source: The name of the stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på den lagrade proceduren.

trans-unit.source: Gets the owner of the stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ägare av den lagrade proceduren.

trans-unit.source: The owner of the stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: Ägaren av den lagrade proceduren.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of parameters required for a stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en samling parametrar som krävs för en lagrad procedur.

trans-unit.source: The Parameters property is populated by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure.CreateParameters%2A> method the first time the Parameters property is accessed.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Parameters fylls den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure.CreateParameters%2A>metoden först gången egenskapen Parameters används.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Data.DesignerDataStoredProcedure.CreateParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: A collection of parameters for the stored procedure.
trans-unit.target: En samling parametrar för den lagrade proceduren.
